      • setOperationTimeout

        public AsyncTableBuilderBase<C> setOperationTimeout(long timeout,
                                                    TimeUnit unit)
        从接口复制的说明: AsyncTableBuilder
        Set timeout for a whole operation such as get, put or delete. Notice that scan will not be effected by this value, see scanTimeoutNs.

        Operation timeout and max attempt times(or max retry times) are both limitations for retrying, we will stop retrying when we reach any of the limitations.

        指定者:
        setOperationTimeout 在接口中 AsyncTableBuilder<C extends ScanResultConsumerBase>
        另请参阅:
        AsyncTableBuilder.setMaxAttempts(int), AsyncTableBuilder.setMaxRetries(int), AsyncTableBuilder.setScanTimeout(long, TimeUnit)

      • setScanTimeout

        public AsyncTableBuilderBase<C> setScanTimeout(long timeout,
                                               TimeUnit unit)
        从接口复制的说明: AsyncTableBuilder
        As now we have heartbeat support for scan, ideally a scan will never timeout unless the RS is crash. The RS will always return something before the rpc timed out or scan timed out to tell the client that it is still alive. The scan timeout is used as operation timeout for every operation in a scan, such as openScanner or next.
        指定者:
        setScanTimeout 在接口中 AsyncTableBuilder<C extends ScanResultConsumerBase>
        另请参阅:
        AsyncTableBuilder.setScanTimeout(long, TimeUnit)

      • setRpcTimeout

        public AsyncTableBuilderBase<C> setRpcTimeout(long timeout,
                                              TimeUnit unit)
        从接口复制的说明: AsyncTableBuilder
        Set timeout for each rpc request.

        Notice that this will NOT change the rpc timeout for read(get, scan) request and write request(put, delete).

        指定者:
        setRpcTimeout 在接口中 AsyncTableBuilder<C extends ScanResultConsumerBase>

      • setMaxAttempts

        public AsyncTableBuilderBase<C> setMaxAttempts(int maxAttempts)
        从接口复制的说明: AsyncTableBuilder
        Set the max attempt times for an operation. Usually it is the max retry times plus 1. Operation timeout and max attempt times(or max retry times) are both limitations for retrying, we will stop retrying when we reach any of the limitations.
        指定者:
        setMaxAttempts 在接口中 AsyncTableBuilder<C extends ScanResultConsumerBase>
        另请参阅:
        AsyncTableBuilder.setMaxRetries(int), AsyncTableBuilder.setOperationTimeout(long, TimeUnit)
